snippet.title: DoctorTale - TARDIS Control Room and Console
snippet.description:
There's a small showcase of our Doctor Who-styled menu. This is the TARDIS control room – a place that I spent a lot of time working on. Here you will change control settings, launch the game and receive various information. We show you the last function here – the rest of them will be improved and showed in future.

GameJolt • • • https://gamejolt.com/games/doctortale/459665
